======================================================================
PART 5: ASYMPTOTIC ANALYSIS
======================================================================

  As n -> inf:
    E2/E0 ~ 2/n -> 0
    E4/E0 ~ 2n^2/(n^4) = 2/n^2 -> 0 (faster)
    E_{2k}/E0 ~ 2n^k/n^{2k} = 2/n^k -> 0
  
    Var/Mean^2 ~ sum_k 2/n^k = 2n/(n-1) * 1/n = 2/(n-1)
    More precisely: Var/Mean^2 = 2/n + 2/n^2 + 2/n^3 + ... = 2/(n-1)
    But this is a HEURISTIC. The actual terms have (n-2k)^k != n^k

  Exact vs 2/(n-1) approximation:
